title: Vicky D'Amour / Coffee Warehouse
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, International, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee bar, bakery, and restaurant. Offers daily vegan choices including burgers, pasta made with yams, soups, a few of the salads, and chili. For dessert you'll find vegan gluten-free cakes and macaroons.
